^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Another interesting bidding problem. The auction is  always down 2. Klau's 4@S bid is aggressive  given the vulnerability in particular. On the minus side, his spades are weak. On the plus side, however, he is short in both our suits. So, it is a bit of a shot, but it could work really well.  Because of the vulnerability and my spade void, I thought 5@C was clearly right. But it turns out it is down 1. As to whether lisa should bid 5@S. The one reason to bid it is she has lots of spades, so it is likely one of us is void. But, there are 3 reasons not to bid it.|
