^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|
- the first is the general rule "the 5 level belongs to the opponents." What that means is, all things being equal (which they never are, lol), you should not bid 5 over 5.
- the second reason is the vulnerability, and
- the third reason, as marge correctly points out, is she has 2 tricks. So if klaus has one trick we are down.|
