^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|lisa plays specific. Let me explain lisa's bid. There are two alternatives to responding to 5N king ask. One is to specify the number of kings 6C =0 , 6D = 1, 6H = 2, 6S = 3. Here, if lisa played that she would have bid 6@C. The other alternative is known as "specific kings"  that means, if lisa has a king, she bids the lowest suit in which she has a king, six of the trump suit otherwise. So, if she had the K of clubs she would bid 6 clubs for example. Playing specific kings, since lisa had no kings she bids 6@H, the trump suit.|
